---
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">
      Fasilitas Program Studi
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Fasilitas pendidikan dirancang untuk mendukung proses pembelajaran, penelitian,
      dan pengembangan kompetensi mahasiswa secara profesional dan berstandar industri.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 px-6">

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-computer-icon lucide-computer"><rect width="14" height="8" x="5" y="2" rx="2"/><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="14" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M6 18h2"/>
          <path d="M12 18h6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800">Laboratorium Komputer</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Prodi Teknik Informatika UIN SUSKA Riau memiliki laboratorium yang dilengkapi dengan peralatan terbaru dan canggih untuk mendukung proses belajar mengajar dan riset para mahasiswa dan dosen.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-monitor-icon lucide-monitor"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="3" rx="2"/><line x1="8" x2="16" y1="21" y2="21"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="17" y2="21"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800">Ruang Kelas</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Prodi Teknik Informatika UIN SUSKA Riau memiliki ruang kelas yang nyaman dilengkapi dengan meja mahasiswa dan dosen serta proyektor untuk mendukung proses belajar mengajar para mahasiswa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wifi-icon lucide-wifi">
          <path d="M12 20h.01"/><path d="M2 8.82a15 15 0 0 1 20 0"/>
          <path d="M5 12.859a10 10 0 0 1 14 0"/>
          <path d="M8.5 16.429a5 5 0 0 1 7 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800">Akses Internet Cepat</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Area kampus dilengkapi Wi-Fi berkecepatan tinggi untuk mendukung kegiatan akademik.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-20 px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 text-center">
      Sistem Layanan Akademik
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

      <a href="https://sireg.uin-suska.ac.id/beranda-sireg-uin-suska-riau.html" 
         class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-md transition text-center">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">SIREG</h3>
      </a>

      <a href="https://iraisenew.uin-suska.ac.id/" 
         class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-md transition text-center">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">iRaise</h3>
      </a>

      <a href="https://elearning.uin-suska.ac.id/login/index.php" 
         class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-md transition text-center">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">E-Learning</h3>
      </a>

      <a href="https://dashboard.tif.uin-suska.ac.id/" 
         class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-md transition text-center">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">Dashboard TIF</h3>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-24 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center p-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-200 to-blue-400 rounded-3xl blur-xl"></div>

      <img src="/aidil11.png"
           alt="Kaprodi Teknik Informatika"
           class="relative z-10 max-h-[420px] object-contain drop-shadow-2xl rounded-2xl"/>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-10 text-gray-800">
      <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mb-2">Universitas Islam Negeri Sultan Syarif Kasim Riau</p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-snug text-blue-900">
        Membentuk Generasi Profesional<br/>
        Berbasis Teknologi & Nilai Keislaman
      </h1>

      <p class="text-base opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
        Program Studi Teknik Informatika memberikan ruang bagi mahasiswa untuk
        mengembangkan kompetensi teknis, kreativitas, dan integritas melalui
        pendidikan yang berbasis sains, inovasi, dan etika.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>
